snippet.title: HONK gameplay
snippet.description:
This is gameplay of HONK. This game I made during Ludum Dare 45 with an artist in 72 hours.

In the distant future, a lonely goose guy is fighting with forces of evil to save the Earth. This eternal battle he faces together with his shotgun.

Kill as many enemies as possible there can be only one who will steal humans stuff.

Ludum Dare page - https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/45/honk
Itch.io - https://tricky-fat-cat.itch.io/honk-ld45
